OL,3,C'The coffin wasn't big enough to hold
OL,4,Cmy stepdad's body'
OL,6,FA woman whose stepfather's body was
OL,7,Fdiscovered months after being told he
OL,8,Fhad been cremated says families
OL,9,Faffected by a funeral business scandal
OL,10,F"feel forgotten".
OL,12,FMichaela Baldwin is among hundreds of
OL,13,Fpeople across East Yorkshire affected
OL,14,Fby the ongoing investigation into
OL,15,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors.
OL,17,FHumberside Police descended on its
OL,18,Fbase in Hessle Road, Hull, in March
OL,19,Fafter they received concerns over care
OL,20,Ffor the deceased.
