OL,3,C'The coffin wasn't big enough to hold
OL,4,Cmy stepdad's body'
OL,6,FOfficers seized 35 bodies and a
OL,7,Fquantity of human ashes linked to a
OL,8,Ffurther 163 families in the region.
OL,10,FAmong those bodies was Ms Baldwin's
OL,11,Fstepfather, who died in November.
OL,13,FThe family paid for him to be cremated
OL,14,Fat Legacy's Hessle Road site.
OL,16,F"When it first came out that was the
OL,17,Ffirst thing that came to my head. He
OL,18,Fwasn't even at his funeral - he can't
OL,19,Fhave been in that coffin," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
