OL,3,C'The coffin wasn't big enough to hold
OL,4,Cmy stepdad's body'
OL,6,F"My stepdad was a big guy - he wasn't
OL,7,Fslim build. We even joked after (the
OL,8,Ffuneral) saying it was too small -
OL,9,Fthat he wasn't in there.
OL,11,F"He'd just been forgotten in my eyes,
OL,12,Fthat's how I see it. He'd just been
OL,13,Fput there and forgotten about."
OL,15,FSix months have now passed since
OL,16,FHumberside Police launched what it
OL,17,Fdescribed as a "complex" investigation.
