OL,3,C'The coffin wasn't big enough to hold
OL,4,Cmy stepdad's body'
OL,6,F"Something has to be put in place to
OL,7,Fstop this happening again. I'd hate
OL,8,Ffor other families to go through this,
OL,9,Fit's one of the worst feelings ever. I
OL,10,Fwouldn't wish it on my worst enemy."
OL,12,FThe ongoing investigation had led to
OL,13,Fcalls for statutory regulation of the
OL,14,Ffuneral industry, which at present
OL,15,Fdoes not exist.
OL,17,FEmma Hardy MP, who represents Hull
OL,18,FWest and Haltemprice and is also a
OL,19,FGovernment minister, has spoken to the
OL,20,FJustice Minister to bring forward a
OL,21,Fconsultation on regulation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
