OL,3,C'The coffin wasn't big enough to hold
OL,4,Cmy stepdad's body'
OL,6,F"We need to get it right, because the
OL,7,Ffuneral sector at the moment there is
OL,8,Fno regulation, there is nothing. So
OL,9,Fthere's no base on which to build,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,F"That consultation process is going to
OL,13,Fbe starting at some point before
OL,14,FChristmas to begin this process. But
OL,15,Fwe've said to people from the very
OL,16,Fbeginning, it will take a long time
OL,17,Fbecause nothing has existed in the
OL,18,Fpast."
